data.description: SELLERS MOTIVATED & Offering $5K Buyer Credit. Bring an offer! This beautifully renovated home offers an ideal location just outside the city limits, while still being a mere 5-minute drive from Downtown Bozeman and 25 mins to Bridger Bowl. Situated on almost half an acre, the property features a fully fenced and private landscaped yard complete with underground sprinklers, mature trees, charming greenhouse, and fully fenced. In Summer 2023, the entire home underwent a professional repainting and new flooring, doors and trim was installed downstairs. The updated kitchen is adorned with reclaimed wood accents, tasteful color combinations, a high-end Aga Stove & Range, a farmhouse sink, beautiful cabinetry, open shelving, and a butcher block center island with seating for three. The main level bedroom suite offers a luxurious bathroom, including a floating soak tub with an accent wall, double vanity, and reclaimed wood accents. Downstairs, you'll find two additional bedrooms, a family room, two full bathrooms, ample storage space, and a convenient laundry/mudroom combo area with a walk-in pantry adjoining the two-car garage. As an added bonus, the home comes with a hot tub on the large outdoor deck! This property has very light covenants and NO HOA dues, allowing for greater flexibility and privacy. The roof was replaced in 2020, and new high-end noise-reducing Marvin brand windows were installed throughout, ensuring both durability and tranquility. With a private well and septic system in place, this home offers self-sufficiency and independence. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home!
